Celeron jumps down onto a piece of metal.  Scanning the area he realizes nothing is around.

"....wasteland"

He continues on.  From the air he spots a crashed ship.  On closer inspection he sees nothing special.  The ship was about 30 cycles old and probably held nothing important.  He cautiously proceeds to find salvage aboard this slag heap.
